---
import ComingSoon from '../layouts/ComingSoon.astro';
---

<ComingSoon title="The Compliance Layer for AI-Generated Code">

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-badge">Coming Soon</div>
    <h1>The compliance layer for<br /><span class="gradient-text">AI-generated code</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Your developers use AI to write code. Who checks if it's compliant?
      Sentrik scans, gates, and traces regulatory compliance automatically
      &mdash; IEC 62304, HIPAA, SOC2, OWASP, and more.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="mailto:hello@sentrik.dev?subject=Demo%20Request&body=I'd%20like%20to%20see%20a%20demo%20of%20Sentrik." class="btn btn-primary">Request a Demo</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Terminal Demo -->
<section class="demo">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="terminal">
      <div class="terminal-header">
        <span class="terminal-dot red"></span>
        <span class="terminal-dot yellow"></span>
        <span class="terminal-dot green"></span>
        <span class="terminal-title">sentrik &mdash; Full Compliance Lifecycle</span>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-body">
        <div id="main-player"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="demo-caption">Real output from a medical device API &mdash; 24 critical findings found, fixed, and gated in minutes</p>

    <div class="demo-tabs">
      <button class="demo-tab active" data-cast="/recordings/05-full-lifecycle.cast">Full Lifecycle</button>
      <button class="demo-tab" data-cast="/recordings/01-init-and-scan.cast">Scan &amp; Findings</button>
      <button class="demo-tab" data-cast="/recordings/02-fix-and-gate.cast">Fix &amp; Gate</button>
      <button class="demo-tab" data-cast="/recordings/03-supply-chain.cast">Dependencies &amp; CVEs</button>
      <button class="demo-tab" data-cast="/recordings/04-compliance.cast">Reports &amp; Evidence</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- The Problem -->
<section class="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">The Problem</h2>
    <div class="problem-grid">
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-stat">70%</div>
        <p>of new code is AI-generated at regulated companies</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-stat">6 weeks</div>
        <p>average time to prepare compliance evidence for a single audit</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-stat">4-5 tools</div>
        <p>required today to cover security + compliance + audit evidence</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-stat">15</div>
        <p>regulatory frameworks covered out of the box, from OWASP to IEC 62304</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- AI Showcase -->
<section class="mcp-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">AI That Writes Compliant Code</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Your AI agent checks compliance rules <em>before</em> writing code. Not after.</p>

    <div class="showcase-block">
      <div class="showcase-text">
        <h3>Compliance During Code Generation</h3>
        <p>Claude Code, Cursor, and VS Code call Sentrik via the Model Context Protocol. The AI asks &ldquo;what rules apply?&rdquo; and writes code that passes the gate on the first try.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-img">
        <img src="/images/mcp-in-action.png" alt="AI agent checking compliance rules during code generation" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="showcase-block reverse">
      <div class="showcase-text">
        <h3>Fix Findings with AI</h3>
        <p>Click any finding, chat with an LLM, and apply the fix &mdash; all from the browser. Compliance officers triage findings without touching an IDE.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-img">
        <img src="/images/ai-chat-panel.png" alt="AI chat panel explaining how to fix a compliance finding" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="showcase-block">
      <div class="showcase-text">
        <h3>Dashboard &amp; Compliance Reports</h3>
        <p>Real-time compliance score, severity trends, scan history, and one-click evidence export for auditors. Everything an auditor needs, generated automatically.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-img">
        <img src="/images/dashboard-overview.png" alt="Sentrik compliance dashboard" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- What It Does -->
<section class="value-props">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">One Tool. Full Compliance Lifecycle.</h2>
    <div class="props-grid">
      <div class="prop-card">
        <div class="prop-icon">&#x26A1;</div>
        <h3>Scan in Seconds</h3>
        <p>386 rules across 15 regulatory frameworks. SQL injection, hardcoded secrets, missing encryption, supply chain risks &mdash; mapped to specific regulatory clauses.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <div class="prop-icon">&#x26D4;</div>
        <h3>Gate Every PR</h3>
        <p>Block non-compliant code in CI/CD. GitHub Actions, Azure Pipelines, GitLab CI. PR comments show exactly which regulation you're violating.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <div class="prop-icon">&#x1F4CB;</div>
        <h3>Audit Evidence in One Click</h3>
        <p>Per-framework compliance reports, trust center pages, evidence bundles, and audit-ready ZIPs. No more 6-week evidence collection sprints.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <div class="prop-icon">&#x1F4E6;</div>
        <h3>Supply Chain Security</h3>
        <p>SBOM generation, CVE scanning, license compliance, secrets detection. Auto-fix vulnerable dependencies and create PRs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <div class="prop-icon">&#x1F517;</div>
        <h3>Full Traceability</h3>
        <p>Requirements &rarr; code &rarr; tests &rarr; work items &rarr; audit evidence. Auto-sync with GitHub, Azure DevOps, and Jira.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <div class="prop-icon">&#x1F3E2;</div>
        <h3>Enterprise Governance</h3>
        <p>Governance profiles, async approval gates, HMAC-signed audit logs, RBAC, auditor portals, and GRC platform integration.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Standards -->
<section class="standards">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">14 Regulatory Frameworks. Built In.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Medical devices, fintech, healthcare, automotive, aviation, embedded systems.</p>
    <div class="standards-grid">
      <div class="standard-card"><h3>IEC 62304</h3><p>Medical device software lifecycle</p></div>
      <div class="standard-card"><h3>OWASP Top 10</h3><p>Web application security</p></div>
      <div class="standard-card"><h3>SOC2</h3><p>Trust services criteria</p></div>
      <div class="standard-card"><h3>HIPAA</h3><p>Healthcare data protection</p></div>
      <div class="standard-card"><h3>PCI DSS</h3><p>Payment card security</p></div>
      <div class="standard-card"><h3>ISO 27001</h3><p>Information security management</p></div>
      <div class="standard-card"><h3>DO-178C</h3><p>Aviation software certification</p></div>
      <div class="standard-card"><h3>ISO 26262</h3><p>Automotive functional safety</p></div>
    </div>
    <p class="section-sub" style="margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem;">Plus MISRA C/C++, ISO 14971, IEC 81001-5-1, 21 CFR Part 11, PHP Security, Kotlin Security</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="cta">
  <div class="container cta-inner">
    <h2>Ready to see it in action?</h2>
    <p class="cta-sub">We're onboarding design partners in medical devices, fintech, and SaaS.</p>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a href="mailto:hello@sentrik.dev?subject=Demo%20Request&body=I'd%20like%20to%20see%20a%20demo%20of%20Sentrik.%0A%0ACompany:%0ARole:%0AFrameworks%20we%20need:%20" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Request a Demo</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</ComingSoon>

<style>
  .hero { padding: 10rem 0 4rem; text-align: center; }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-accent));
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .hero h1 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 3.2rem; line-height: 1.15; }
  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-light), var(--color-accent));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; }
  .btn-lg { padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }

  .screenshot { width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }

  .demo { padding: 2rem 0 4rem; }
  .terminal { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); }
  .terminal-header { background: #2d2640; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .terminal-dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; }
  .terminal-dot.red { background: #ff5f57; }
  .terminal-dot.yellow { background: #ffbd2e; }
  .terminal-dot.green { background: #28c840; }
  .terminal-title { margin-left: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; }
  .terminal-body { background: #1a1428; padding: 0; overflow: hidden; }
  .demo-caption { text-align: center; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-top: 1.25rem; font-style: italic; }
  .demo-tabs { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1.25rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .demo-tab { padding: 0.5rem 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem; font-family: var(--font-sans); font-weight: 500; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 8px; background: var(--color-surface); color: var(--color-text-muted); cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s ease; }
  .demo-tab:hover { border-color: var(--color-primary); color: var(--color-text); }
  .demo-tab.active { border-color: var(--color-primary); background: var(--color-primary); color: #fff; }
  #main-player { min-height: 300px; }
  :global(.ap-wrapper) { border-radius: 0 !important; }

  /* Problem stats */
  .problem { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .problem-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .problem-card { background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; }
  .problem-stat { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .problem-card p { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* Showcase */
  .mcp-section { padding: 5rem 0; background: var(--color-bg-alt); }
  .section-title { text-align: center; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .section-sub { text-align: center; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .showcase-block { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .showcase-block.reverse { direction: rtl; }
  .showcase-block.reverse > * { direction: ltr; }
  .showcase-text h3 { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .showcase-text p { color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }

  /* Value props */
  .value-props { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .props-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .prop-card { background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .prop-card:hover { border-color: var(--color-primary); }
  .prop-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .prop-card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .prop-card p { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; }

  /* Standards */
  .standards { padding: 5rem 0; background: var(--color-bg-alt); }
  .standards-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1rem; }
  .standard-card { background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .standard-card:hover { border-color: var(--color-primary); }
  .standard-card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .standard-card p { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; }

  /* CTA */
  .cta { padding: 6rem 0; text-align: center; }
  .cta h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .cta-sub { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
    .problem-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .showcase-block, .showcase-block.reverse { grid-template-columns: 1fr; direction: ltr; }
    .props-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .standards-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    .problem-grid, .props-grid, .standards-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
